or the People Act），称如果它完全通过，“将毁灭选举的公平性，让民主党人永远掌权，摧毁我们的宪法”。 据复旦发展研究院发表的分析文章称，《为人民法案》是一个降低选举权门槛的法案。因为固有的选举流程过于繁琐，导致低收入街区和少数族裔投票率太低。这项法案是由民主党提出的，而在众议院针对该法案的投票表决中，209位出席的共和党议员都投了反对票。 此外，公开信还质疑美国总统拜登的身心健康状况。信中称，“这位统帅的身心健康状况不容忽视。他必须能够无论白天黑夜，能在任何地方快速、准确地作出涉及国家安全问题的决策”、“我们必须得拥有无可置疑的指挥系统”。 但据《商业内幕》（Business Insider）报道称，在本月早些时候，拜登的医师凯文·奥康纳(Kevin O'Connor)发布了一份有关拜登健康状况的报告，报告中称拜登“健康、充满活力”、“能够胜任总统一职”。"},"attached_info":"Cj8IlPai0L3Nj9dBEAMaCDY0MzgzODM0IKGL+oQGMB841QZAA3IJNDU5NDY2MDg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"1044 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9dbdfa472d262fe7180832463f0aafd7_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"4_1621062822.320979","card_id":"Q_459271480","target":{"id":459271480,"title":"当老板说『你上班只是为了钱吗 』，应该如何回答？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/459271480","type":"question","created":1620908852,"answer_count":570,"follower_count":1375,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1537,1575,2566,4761,5582],"comment_count":55,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"图片来自于网络"},"attached_info":"Cj8IlPai0L3Nj9dBEAMaCDY0MzQwNjE4ILS29IQGMDc43wpABHIJNDU5MjcxNDgweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"831 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-3b64e069aab42e637160a8b6febfb80d_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1621062822.3214247","card_id":"Q_63812554","target":{"id":63812554,"title":"如何看待当下白瘦幼的主流审美？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/63812554","type":"question","created":1502545147,"answer_count":2271,"follower_count":7616,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[10490,163137],"comment_count":240,"is_following":f